### 1. `app/include/ms_colibri_command_interface.h` — header refactor

Replace the contents. Keep the three `#pragma pack`ed structs (`__colibri_message_command`, `__colibri_message_ack`, `__colibri_message_full_ack`) — the byte layouts match the PDF. Remove the global `double k = …` (move to `ms_colibri_command_interface.cc` as `static constexpr double K_RATE`). Move encode/decode and checksum functions to the .cc; declare them in the header as free functions.

Add message-name constants at the top of the header (matching the `mMAVLINK_*` style):
