#define mCOLIBRI_ACK_FIXED        "colibri_ack_fixed"      // 20-byte slow-mode ack
#define mCOLIBRI_ACK_FULL         "colibri_ack_full"       // 64-byte fast-mode full ack
```

Rewrite the class to match `mavlink_interface`:
```cpp
